item.title: am
item.description: 9:58am CDT Saturday 27 July 2002 Awake. Unpacking and repacking my car to go visit the Bibby's for a few days. Ironically, Sean is in Utah now, so I can't hang out with him exactly yet. 4:52pm Been chillin' with Janette, Sean and Joey's mom. Joey just woke up a bit ago. Janette has been cooking all day ("20 hours" she says) and I've helped a tiny bit by cutting parsley (I think) and jalepenos and mixing tabouli.
